  <entry>
    <title>Python IDLE修改代码配色及语法高亮主题</title>
    <link href="https://guoke.co/python-idle-theme/" />
    <id>https://guoke.co/python-idle-theme/</id>
    <updated>2024-10-03T00:48:16Z</updated>
    <author>
      <name>dodopoi</name>
    </author>
    <summary type="html">
      
    </summary>
    
    <content type="html">
      <![CDATA[
      <p>找到名为<strong>config-highlight.cfg</strong>的文件，在Windows 7下路径为：<code>C:\Users\&lt;用户名&gt;\.idlerc\</code>如果没有就新建一个。</p>
<pre><code class="language-sh">[tango]
definition-foreground = #fce94f
error-foreground = #fa8072
string-background = #2e3436
keyword-foreground = #8cc4ff
normal-foreground = #ffffff
comment-background = #2e3436
hit-foreground = #ffffff
break-foreground = #000000
